WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:06.000
NYU is fully committed to the well-being of our students, and we will do everything we can to make sure a student's experience is both academically and socially fulfilling

00:07.000 --> 00:12.000
However, should a student decide that the campus at which they matriculate is not the right fit for him or her, a request for a change of campus will be given consideration

00:13.000 --> 00:18.000
If a request for change of campus is approved, the Financial Aid office will evaluate a student's financial circumstances in the context of financial aid packages offered at the new campus

00:19.000 --> 00:24.000
Financial aid packages vary greatly among our three campuses, so students should be aware of this reality should transferring become a consideration

